Ain't no darkness,
under your wing.
Ain't no secrets,
in the way you ring.

Do love come by chance?
a child of circumstance.

Perhaps I should not think,
close my eyes and drink.

Ain't no ,
holding your hand.



There is sunshine,
under your feet.
There is moonlight,
on our street.


